import { Box, Card, CardContent, Typography } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

export default function UsersComponent(props) {
    const { gitUsers } = props;

    console.log(gitUsers)
    return (
        <Box style={{display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center', marginTop: '2rem'}}>
            <Card>
                <CardContent>
                    <Box>
                        <Typography variant="h4" component="h4" style={{textAlign: 'center'}}>
                            Git User Info Search Result
                        </Typography>
                    </Box>
                </CardContent>
            </Card>
        </Box>
    )
}
